4Geeks Academy offers a Full Stack Developer Bootcamp designed for individuals aspiring to enter the tech industry. The program spans 18 weeks, teaching essential technologies such as JavaScript and Python. Students will engage in three classes weekly, with a low student-to-instructor ratio of 7:1. There are no prerequisites, making it accessible to everyone, and the curriculum is available in both English and Spanish. The bootcamp culminates in a personal project, providing hands-on experience. Graduates receive a Full-Stack Developer certificate. For more details, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/part-time-full-stack-developer). stop